Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.46,0:00:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,De ce spun dintr-odată povestea asta?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:28.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Treaba mea era doar să simulez un interviu cu Mernes ca să-l ajut cu abilitătile sale de comunicare...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.50,0:02:12.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Deci...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:13.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Da?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:17.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ai spus că vrei să ni te alături ca să distrugi umanitatea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:20.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Dar asta e o minciună, nu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.71,0:02:31.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Credeam că voi primi această întrebare de la Shutina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.54,0:02:33.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sunt surprins că vine de la tine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:39.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tu mi-ai spus: "See it from their point of view,\Nfigure out what they want to talk about."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.58,0:02:41.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Deci m-am pus în locul tău.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.71,0:02:45.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Și atunci mi-am dat seama de ceva.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:51.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nu ai nevoie de noi. Poți distruge umanitatea de unul singur.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:59.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Păi, dacă poți empatiza atât de bine, ești deja un maestru în comunicare.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:04.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,În regulă, îti voi da o diplomă! Oare unde am pus-o?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:09.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, here, I've got ten meal tickets for\Nthe Rat Restaurant! Congrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nu încerca să schimbi subiectul.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:15.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,De ce nu i-ai distrus până acum?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:18.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're preachin' to the choir, bud! Why haven't I, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:19.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Stop playing dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:21.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Careful with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Nu erai furios?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.17,0:03:35.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You gave your all to protect them,\Nand they threw you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Ți-ai riscat viața luptând împotriva noastră.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You never just wanted them all dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.04,0:03:43.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.08,0:03:47.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mi-ai cercetat trecutul, nu-i așa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:53.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Da, puțin. Știu că ești jumătate om, jumătate demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:04:00.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oamenii se temeau de tine, deci părinții tăi te-au vândut drept sclav
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.38,0:04:05.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,și după ce ai slujit diferiți stăpâni, ai fost cumpărat de Breasla Asasinilor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.71,0:04:06.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Așa e.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:13.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The guild thought I'd be expendable,\Nthat I'd die taking out my first and only target.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.96,0:04:16.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But for better or for worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.46,0:04:21.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was a good enough assassin to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:23.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,deserve to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:29.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why I was more than supportive\Nof the Demon Army's invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:35.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I so desperately wanted them\Nto finish off humanity once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Your Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:50.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've startling news! The castle gates have opened for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:57.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Very well. Do not let this chance escape us!\NAll troops, move in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:08.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I raced ahead of their forces and\Nsecretly gave them my assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.63,0:05:10.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.21,0:05:31.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fear not! We have not come to slaughter you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:36.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our objective lies in the Capital, in Renailles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:41.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We will rebuild the town as we use it\Nas our new base of operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.83,0:05:44.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've also captured your corrupt mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:51.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There was so much food in his castle!\NLet's share it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:57.79,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Okay, line up! Don't worry, there's enough for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:59.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why didn't we kill them? It was a waste of precious time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:07.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Despite my doubts, I made contact with Echidna,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and joined the army under false pretenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.50,0:06:16.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we leave this town and proceed forward?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.83,0:06:18.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.25,0:06:22.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Tonight, though, the populace is providing us\Nwith a grand welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:31.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've liberated us and restored peace.\NWe can't thank you enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.50,0:06:34.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Think nothing of it.\NIt was a necessary part of our own plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:39.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is good! You should try this!\NDoes anyone want refills on juice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:43.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is crazy! We're in the middle of an invasion,\Nhosting a grand feast?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:50.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I understand your frustration, but this, too,\Nis part of Queen Echidna's strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.79,0:06:54.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Non-stop fighting will lead to burned-out troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.42,0:06:57.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This creates the opportunity\Nfor them to refresh themselves
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.96,0:07:03.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and for her to speak one-on-one with\Nher subordinates, reigniting their motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:05.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Their motivation?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.08,0:07:07.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You've been working hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I-I'm honored that you've noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:12.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.83,0:07:16.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Our Queen is a strange one, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:23.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Before I joined up, I thought the Army was\Nan evil force hell-bent on destroying humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:28.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why when they asked me to join, I said no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:36.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There are horrible humans, true,\Nbut that don't mean they all deserve to burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:40.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But then I saw that this is who they really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:46.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Besides, no man or woman who\Nloves good ale can be a villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:48.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:56.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernes, why did you join the Demon Army?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:01.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I couldn't tell them I'd joined with\Nthe hopes of slaughtering humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.17,0:08:04.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.58,0:08:08.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Mernes, I'm glad to have you among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll be needing your help again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:17.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Once we have the Philosopher's Stone,\Nand the Demon World has become a paradise,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I invite you to join us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.08,0:08:21.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I expect you'd like living somewhere peaceful and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:27.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:29.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh? Leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.25,0:08:32.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Aww, I wanted to hang out with you though!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:33.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.46,0:08:40.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If I need to, I'll take out Echidna and\Nlead the Demon Army myself to destroy humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:47.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,After that, I became one of the Great Generals,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.63,0:08:53.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and half-heartedly helped lead its brilliant forces\Nthrough its successful campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:57.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Well, successful until SOMEONE came along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.58,0:08:59.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:02.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Remember what I said that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.13,0:09:14.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've lost. Kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:18.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you don't, then someday, I'll exterminate humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.71,0:09:24.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. You're acting like you've never seen\Nanything cool in your whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:29.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Go out and see the world a little, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:31.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.08,0:09:34.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I've done that, and I'm bored of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:39.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,This world sucks. Nothing in it is 'cool'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.46,0:09:43.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's because you've only seen it as an assassin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.75,0:09:51.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The world looks different when you're seeing it\Non your own terms, not just for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.67,0:09:53.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As if it's that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.67,0:09:56.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not like I'd know that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:09:57.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:00.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,In any case, here's my advice for you right now:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.63,0:10:04.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Go seek out something in the world you've never seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,If you still want to die after that, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:12.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, and if you do something evil, I'll kill you too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:13.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.50,0:10:23.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You spouted off all those high-and-mighty words,\Nso why'd you decide to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.42,0:10:26.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To destroy humanity? I know that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.46,0:10:29.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't care what happens to humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:34.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But you don't seem to have, the, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.50,0:10:36.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The hatred for mankind?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:40.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You've got something else going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:43.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Else, you wouldn't have said all that stuff to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:46.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.58,0:10:51.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,They betrayed you. Normally people\Nget angry when they're betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:55.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You get sad, you hate them, you truly start to hate them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:56.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:11:02.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm learning way too many new things\Nabout these guys now that I've joined them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:07.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The prim and proper Shutina is a klutz\Nwho barely keeps herself afloat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:11.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The brainless wild child is a diligent, good kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And now we've got Mernes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:20.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The uncaring, unfeeling assassin\Nstruggles with teenage angst.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:26.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The reason he kept quiet after hearing my reasons for\Njoining wasn't that he didn't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.33,0:11:32.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He heard how I'd been exiled by humanity\Nand felt for me from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:37.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, man, don't cry. Now I feel like it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:39.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.67,0:11:44.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll listen, so just tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:56.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:12:03.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, getting told "we don't need you" and\N"kill the hero" made me feel pretty shitty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.42,0:12:04.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:07.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Especially since I've been defending\Nhumanity for a long, long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,How long...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.25,0:12:10.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:13.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Let me tell you what the world was like when I was born.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:15.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It was a long, long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:17.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What am I telling him this for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:23.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,At the height of industrial civilization,\Nbefore magic came into common use.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.33,0:12:26.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The land was shaped a bit differently than it is now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:31.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and where the Capital now stands,\Nthere stood the city of Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We launched rockets into the sea of stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:42.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,encircled the earth with swarms of man-made satellites,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:46.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and an invisible, high-speed communication\Nnetwork connected the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:49.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,There were tensions, but mostly peace,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:54.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and unlike our diverse world,\Nmine was made up of only humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:02.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A hole opened up in the middle of Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.00,0:13:18.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,From it came imps, dwarves, orcs,\Ngoblins, succubi and incubi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:21.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All manner of demons we're well-acquainted with now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:26.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Back then, we just called them "demons".
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.04,0:13:31.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just like Echidna, they were sick of the dark,\Nhorrific Demon World,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.67,0:13:36.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and came to the human world\Nseeking its warmth and light.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.63,0:13:41.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Many tried to peacefully exist alongside humanity,\Nbut others opted for violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:44.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What was humanity going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:46.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Fight back, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:50.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What had started on an eastern island nation\Nspread around the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.75,0:13:54.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,and it wasn't long until there was a full-out world\Nwar on demon kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:57.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And sadly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:14:00.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Humans back then were as weak as they are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:04.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It took dozens of humans just to get rid of one demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:06.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We need stronger weapons!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:11.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yes, an unstoppable weapon that can\Nprotect humanity from this demonic threat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.67,0:14:14.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Now is the time for humanity to join as one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.71,0:14:19.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,To kill a demon, we must create a demon ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The project is nearly complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:26.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,We've used the demon's own power\Nto forge twelve powerful weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.96,0:14:31.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,living beings with limitless potential\Nto evolve, grow, and protect humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:33.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The Demonhart Series!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.33,0:14:35.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As of now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:38.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,only one Demonhart survives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.04,0:14:41.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're a living weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:48.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wh-what the hell does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.17,0:14:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,From the moment I was born, I was a hero.\NI knew no other way of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:15:03.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,My orders were planted at inception:\NProtect humanity. Save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.38,0:15:09.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,All heroes grow old and die,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:13.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,but I was made to be extremely durable and long-lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.46,0:15:20.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The other DH Series models fell in battle, one by one,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,leaving me as the only surviving hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:30.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'll put it this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:35.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd missed my chance to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:43.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even after the industrial world fell, and magic\Nreplaced machinery, I went on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:47.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It happened so long ago, I can barely remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:52.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Whenever war erupted, I was there to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.83,0:15:56.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd grown too strong to die in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:02.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Protect humanity. Save the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.54,0:16:07.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those were my orders,\Nbut were they the right things to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:09.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Was I just keeping humanity dependent on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:20.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No one could answer those questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.17,0:16:22.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:25.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Not like I'd know that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:29.58,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't abandon my duty to protect the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.50,0:16:36.54,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,When the world pushed me aside just recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:39.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,sure, I was a little sad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:45.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't upset about it. In fact...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.21,0:16:47.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.17,0:16:50.42,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,But why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:55.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I WAS happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.88,0:16:59.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:04.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Those warm words of "we don't need you"\Nand "let's kill him"...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:11.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,...were the most meaningful words I'd ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:15.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It finally gave me a chance to quit heroing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.38,0:17:23.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't have to protect humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.92,0:17:28.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,The next time humanity needs protection,\NI can just do whatever I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:34.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I can be myself. Go see the parts of the world\NI want to see, on my own terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.67,0:17:43.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So I'm spending my 'second' life doing\Nwhat I always wanted: joining the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.25,0:17:43.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:46.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Echidna didn't just get up and\Ngo back to the demon world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:50.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You know her father, Demon King Cychreus?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.46,0:17:53.21,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I don't understand a single thing you've said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:56.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He wasted NO time going home.\NDidn't even get a chance to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:17:56.88,Subtitle-3,,0,0,0,,I said, hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:01.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Why did I tell him all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.54,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,You know how the saying goes,\Na good communicator is a good listener!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.88,0:18:04.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:07.54,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,Once people know you're a good listener,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.67,0:18:09.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I just wanted someone to hear my story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:12.46,Subtitle-2,,0,0,0,,they'll start coming to you, asking to vent or to get some advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.04,0:18:15.63,Subtitle-4,,0,0,0,,Don't hold it in. Talk it out, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:20.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I assumed some good listener out there\Nwould ask me about it someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.75,0:18:26.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Who knew it'd end up being you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:28.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You're not making sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:33.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Demon King Cychreus invaded hundreds of years ago,\Naccording to the legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.38,0:18:37.46,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Yep. And according to legend,\Na 'mysterious sage' saved the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.46,0:18:38.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:41.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,What? How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.54,0:18:43.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,No, first...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:45.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,WHAT are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:51.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Just an ex-hero they built to be\Na bit tougher than the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,As for how old I am... No idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:56.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I stopped counting when I passed a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:57.75,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,A THOUSAND?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.13,0:19:02.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Man, though, you live this long, you meet a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:09.38,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You meet one person you want to protect with your life,\Nthen another you want to see dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So believe me when I say this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:13.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You guys are a good lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.50,0:19:19.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Echidna and the Great Guardians\Nare all big goofballs, but they're good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:23.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good enough to make me want\Nto work my butt off for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.33,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Goofballs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:34.00,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So don't worry. I'll get that\NPhilosopher's Stone for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:38.25,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure you all find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.38,0:19:41.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.71,0:19:47.83,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I still don't get it. And you're not going\Nto explain any further, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:50.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'll get around to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.38,0:19:54.04,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I mean, I hadn't planned on telling you all this, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:56.13,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,So why'd you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:20:00.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Because you looked serious, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:05.63,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'd felt this since that moment at the lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:12.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He's not the best talker, but he's got the\None thing that makes you a good communicator:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.33,0:20:15.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Turn me into a master communicator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.29,0:20:17.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Strong motivation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:23.29,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That genuine desire is the most\Nimportant part of communicating well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.21,0:20:31.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You might be blunt and awkward,\Nbut I could tell you really wanted to hear me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:35.67,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,That's why I couldn't stop myself\Nfrom telling you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.58,0:20:41.92,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You just need to be genuine and thoughtful,\Njust like you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.54,0:20:48.79,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You'll do great in your interviews. I know\Nyou'll be able to get the applicants to open up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.04,0:20:51.50,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.83,0:20:54.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,I'm done, and I'm tired. I'm going to pass out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.96,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on, you've got your own room!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.96,0:21:00.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,And we've got another long day in the cafeteria\Ntomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.08,0:21:01.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:04.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mernes! Don't pass out on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.88,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.29,0:21:23.17,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,You never change, though, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.17,0:21:45.08,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,He might be able to mediate.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.63,0:23:33.71,Subtitle,,0,0,0,,Oh, father...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:06.79,Caption,signs,0,0,0,,The Hero Shares His Tale of Burden
